1. *Pravio* sam sendvič za ručak. (I made a sandwich for lunch.)
2. On *pravi* kulu od peska na plaži. (He is building a sandcastle on the beach.)
3. Oni su *pravili* kolače celog popodneva. (They were making cakes all afternoon.)
4. Kada sam bio mlad, *pravio* sam mnogo grešaka. (When I was young, I made a lot of mistakes.)
5. *Pravite* li nešto posebno za vikend? (Are you making anything special for the weekend?)
6. Moj deda je *pravio* nameštaj svojim rukama. (My grandfather made furniture with his own hands.)
7. Ne bih želela da *pravim* probleme, ali moram da kažem istinu. (I don't want to make trouble, but I have to tell the truth.)
8. On *pravi* planove za sledeći put kad dođemo ovde. (He is making plans for the next time we come here.)
9. *Pravljenje* pice je lako kada imate pravu recepturu. (Making pizza is easy when you have the right recipe.)
10. Često *pravimo* istu grešku, iako znamo bolje. (We often make the same mistake, even though we know better.)